name: bübütü
description:
bübütü is half Pampas Cat half human, small, sneaky and smart. she has the thunder power.
don't destroy the nature, if you don't want to feel her fierce and rage.

bübütü means rain in Bororo's language, Boe Wadáru. Bororo is a brazilian original people who lives in the Mato Grosso state.

support and know about the indigenous rights.
acess: https://apiboficial.org/
#PL490Não #ForaBolsonaro #IndigenousLivesMatter
